sea-outpost-after-ships-collide?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国利用液化天然气冷能进行高端海鲜养殖，旨在减少对海外的依赖</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3255573/china-harnesses-lng-cold-energy-high-end-seafood-cultivation-aims-reduce-overseas-reliance?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在中国努力减少对海鲜进口的依赖之际，深圳的试点项目利用液化天然气冷能养殖石斑鱼、龙虾和鲍鱼等高价值海洋物种。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 04:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3255573/china-harnesses-lng-cold-energy-high-end-seafood-cultivation-aims-reduce-overseas-reliance?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>习近平在“平躺运动”前告诉中纪委，中国官员没有做好斗争准备</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3255597/china-officials-unprepared-struggle-xi-jinping-told-ccdi-ahead-lying-flat-campaign?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在刚刚发表的对共产党纪检部门的讲话中，中国领导人表示，许多干部缺乏残酷斗争的磨炼。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 02:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3255597/china-officials-unprepared-struggle-xi-jinping-told-ccdi-ahead-lying-flat-campaign?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者希望出售或禁止 TikTok，但中国字节跳动不会不战而屈人之兵</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3255539/us-lawmakers-want-tiktok-sale-or-ban-chinas-bytedance-wont-give-without-fight?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>夹在华盛顿和北京的要求之间，字节跳动选择了在美国的抵抗路线。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 02:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3255539/us-lawmakers-want-tiktok-sale-or-ban-chinas-bytedance-wont-give-without-fight?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国的“新生产力”计划应该让西方刮目相看</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3255248/why-chinas-plan-new-productive-forces-should-make-west-sit?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>它是被严重低估的“中国制造2025”战略的后继者，该战略催生了中国在电动汽车、绿色科技和其他高端产业的主导地位。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 01:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3255248/why-chinas-plan-new-productive-forces-should-make-west-sit?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国国防增加印太威慑预算，中国成为美国关注的焦点</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3255534/china-americas-sights-us-defence-increases-its-budget-indo-pacific-deterrence?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>专家表示，潜艇建造和核威慑预计将成为美国未来一年国防的核心问题。</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 00:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3255534/china-americas-sights-us-defence-increases-its-budget-indo-pacific-deterrence?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟批准有关回收和人权的法律可能严重影响与中国的贸易</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3255622/eu-approves-laws-recycling-and-human-rights-may-sharply-affect-trade-china?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>欧盟成员国批准了一系列法律，包括要求大型企业对其海外供应商进行人权和环境审计。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 16:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3255622/eu-approves-laws-recycling-and-human-rights-may-sharply-affect-trade-china?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着华盛顿打压中国企业，他们的游说者受到攻击</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3255590/washington-cracks-down-chinese-businesses-their-lobbyists-come-under-fire?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>对北京可能威胁美国国家安全的担忧促使多项法案出台，要求对谁代表中国利益进行更严格的审查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3255590/washington-cracks-down-chinese-businesses-their-lobbyists-come-under-fire?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>腾讯与清华大学和香港科技大学合作推出全新人工智能视频生成工具，让静态图像栩栩如生</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3255602/tencents-new-ai-video-generation-tool-brings-static-images-life-collaboration-tsinghua-and-hkust?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>Follow-Your-Click 是与香港和北京大学的研究人员共同开发的，在 Sora 的大肆宣传下，将图像和简单的文本提示变成短视频剪辑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3255602/tencents-new-ai-video-generation-tool-brings-static-images-life-collaboration-tsinghua-and-hkust?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部从新疆聘请新新闻官员</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3255587/chinas-foreign-ministry-brings-new-press-official-xinjiang?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>林健曾任国营准军事组织兵团对外办公室党委书记。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3255587/chinas-foreign-ministry-brings-new-press-official-xinjiang?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着气候变化对贫困农民的可可作物造成影响，巧克力的价格是多少？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/world/article/3255429/what-price-chocolate-climate-change-hits-cocoa-crops-poor-farmers?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>由于可可作物面临生存挑战，而需求持续激增（包括来自中国的需求），巧克力将保持昂贵的价格。当务之急是在不损害环境的情况下种植可可，并确保可可种植者能够在此过程中摆脱贫困。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/world/article/3255429/what-price-chocolate-climate-change-hits-cocoa-crops-poor-farmers?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴在华为鸿蒙操作系统中添加了 11 个应用程序，为中国的 Android 竞争对手带来了闲鱼、飞猪等应用程序</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3255568/alibaba-adds-11-apps-huaweis-harmonyos-bringing-xianyu-fliggy-and-more-chinas-android-rival?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>阿里巴巴将为菜鸟快递服务和外卖应用程序饿了么等平台开发原生 HarmonyOS 应用程序。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3255568/alibaba-adds-11-apps-huaweis-harmonyos-bringing-xianyu-fliggy-and-more-chinas-android-rival?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国国家主导的产业政策是否正走在一条危险的道路上？一些北京顾问警告称存在“有害”影响</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3255547/chinas-state-led-industrial-policy-perilous-path-some-beijing-advisers-warn-detrimental-implications?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>向替代能源等战略产业注入资金使中国在国际竞争中占据了巨大优势，但国内专家表示，问题可能正在显现。</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3255547/chinas-state-led-industrial-policy-perilous-path-some-beijing-advisers-warn-detrimental-implications?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>